hing and housing.  See all Pembina Trails' Human Rights Project galleries at https://www.creatubbles.com/schools/11\",\"created_at\":\"2015-03-25T08:19:47.410Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2015-11-08T07:13:21.978Z\",\"last_bubbled_at\":null,\"last_commented_at\":null,\"creations_count\":678,\"bubbles_count\":0,\"comments_count\":0,\"short_url\":\"https://staging.ctbl.es/UUPk8Utx\",\"banner\":{\"links\":{\"original\":\"/galleries/covers/290/a46728d5-7e7a-41da-9751-9c86689d879e.jpg\",\"header_retina\":\"/galleries/covers/290/header_retina_a46728d5-7e7a-41da-9751-9c86689d879e.jpg\",\"header\":\"/galleries/covers/290/header_a46728d5-7e7a-41da-9751-9c86689d879e.jpg\",\"thumb_retina\":\"/galleries/covers/290/thumb_retina_a46728d5-7e7a-41da-9751-9c86689d879e.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"/galleries/covers/290/thumb_a46728d5-7e7a-41da-9751-9c86689d879e.jpg\"}},\"preview_image_urls\":[\"https://d3fll5fltyv3n9.cloudfront.net/users/4206/creations/18522/matrix_view_retina/1446249680creation.jpg\",\"https://d3fll5fltyv3n9.cloudfront.net/users/16676/creations/11278/matrix_view_retina/1431698429creation.jpg\",\"https://d3fll5fltyv3n9.cloudfront.net/users/21135/creations/11234/matrix_view_retina/1431651629creation.jpg\",\"https://d3fll5fltyv3n9.cloudfront.net/users/21099/creations/11235/matrix_view_retina/1431651889creation.jpg\"],\"bubbled_by_user_ids\":[]}},{\"id\":\"ghlNo5AN\",\"type\":\"galleries\",\"attributes\":{\"name\":\"A00 - UN Convention on the Rights of the Child\",\"description\":\"âRights\\\" are things every child should have or be able to do. All children have the same rights. These rights are listed in the UN Convention on the Rights of the Child. Almost every country has agreed to these rights. All the rights are connected to each other, and all are equally\\r\\nimportant. Sometimes, we have to think about rights in terms of what is the best for children in a situation, and what is critical to life and protection from harm. As you grow, you have more responsibility to make choices an